  "method": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over the medium heat.",
    "Add onion, green, and red bell pepper; stir frequently. Cook for 6-8",
    "minutes.",
    "Add cumin, salt, and chili powder.",
    "Add shrimp and cook for 3-5 minutes.",
    "Turn off the heat.",
    "Add lime juice and jalapeno pepper in shrimp mixture.",
    "Heat a pan over the medium heat; brush it with vegetable oil.",
    "Put a tortilla in it. Place shrimp filling and cheese blend on it, and",
    "then fold the tortilla.",
    "Cook each side for around 5 minutes.",
    "Repeat the same process with all tortillas.",
    "Serve and enjoy!"
